      <title>One of the most beautiful exhibitions I’ve seen in a long time — L’Empire du som...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DTsB3gojV7_/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DTsB3gojV7_/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/619765738_1149774400361091_3876132327877190145_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=110&amp;ig_cache_key=MzgxMzQzMTE5NzEzMzc5MDk3NQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2LnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=SYAzoS3Z4AQQ7kNvwGjLvlV&amp;_nc_oc=Adp6_5Wq9z_3sXigBD6EOzVeUiHIHMcw7mk-YDYiFt588rp_U9HRyTyBwxgRnvFJsVs&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=febizekAl35KLUHp8QiyzQ&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfwUovryOW1tT7C3ZezXoh_iav3y0NEkPC4hJXc-Zwo7Cw&amp;oe=69CA03CD" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @balder_olrik" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@balder_olrik</strong></p><p>One of the most beautiful exhibitions I’ve seen in a long time — L’Empire du sommeil at the Musée Marmottan Monet  (16th arrondissement, metro La Muette). 🌙<br/>
A quiet, dreamlike journey through how painters have imagined sleep:  from Goya’s nightmares to Füssli’s strange visions, Sorolla’s luminous rest, Previati’s soft reveries, and the oneiric worlds of Picasso, Grandville, and Klinger.<br/>
Every room felt like a different kind of sleep — unsettling, tender, or suspended somewhere between night and waking.<br/>
 On view until March 1, 2026.  If you’re in Paris, don’t miss it. ✨</p><p><a href="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t16/f2/m69/AQN7xH3lGPo2aIx36bbcQJrkSZbUazj5WRf4K9cEWQbMnT-ar6bMC2uUs8f-_8LlA672hibv0gknIPDcZ3V7Mt4i.mp4?strext=1&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=5e9851&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_ohc=XKpyNc09FTIQ7kNvwGw07_i&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTg1NTg1MDEwNjEwMjg5NDQsImFzc2V0X2FnZV9kYXlzIjo2NSwidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjU2LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&amp;ccb=17-1&amp;vs=1a40b6136701943d&amp;_nc_&amp;_nc_gid=febizekAl35KLUHp8QiyzQ&amp;_nc_zt=28&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfzCEg5_QBglmc9MgRWXuCYm8w3iFTsT1vDHZEmz7m5VFQ&amp;oe=69C9FA57">▶️ Åbn video direkte</a> · <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DTsB3gojV7_/">se på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
